    <video youtube="ZEaKBanUbLk" />
  </paragraphs>
  <paragraphs>
    <title>Post-video reflection</title>
    <p>For a rational function, what is the key thing to check before we just "plug the value in" and say that <m>\displaystyle\lim_{x\to a}f(x)=f(a)</m>?</p>
  </paragraphs>

